Hello Zardus

::  Wolfgang steps back, a little weiry of what the misinformed bot might do
::
______________________________________________________________

:: Rainchark ::

:: Rainchark arrives at the base (NDE).  He speaks in a loud, booming voice,
making sure that if anyone was inside, they would hear him ::

I need help.
________________________________________________________________

:: Reptilica walks out of CR chamber and walks towards the bridge.  He sees
